# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:20
translate portuguese tammy16_39bb639d:

    # tm "Oh hey, [pcname]!"
    tm "Oh, olá, [pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:22
translate portuguese tammy16_c7aa7331:

    # tm "I wanted to let you know that I got another fight!"
    tm "Queria dizer-te que tenho mais um combate!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:23
translate portuguese tammy16_46fcf508:

    # pc "Oh yeah? Awesome!"
    pc "Ah, sim? Fantástico!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:25
translate portuguese tammy16_537005d0:

    # tm "Yeah! I mean, it's the same opponent. Sara Death."
    tm "Sim! Quer dizer, é a mesma adversária. A Sara Death."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:26
translate portuguese tammy16_ff4ca977:

    # tm "They couldn't find anybody else to fight me around here."
    tm "Não conseguiram encontrar mais ninguém por aqui para lutar contra mim."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:27
translate portuguese tammy16_c040e3a2:

    # pc "Still. A rematch! That'll be fun."
    pc "Mesmo assim. Uma revanche! Vai ser divertido."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:29
translate portuguese tammy16_65a45e79:

    # tm "Yeah, so it's Friday evening. You're going to come, right?"
    tm "Sim, então é sexta-feira à noite. Vais vir, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:30
translate portuguese tammy16_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:31
translate portuguese tammy16_0d0b0b78:

    # tm "Good. Suzy's coming to this one too."
    tm "Ótimo. A Suzy também vai a esta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:33
translate portuguese tammy16_a716e406:

    # tm "I'm so fucking excited!"
    tm "Estou tão entusiasmada!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:34
translate portuguese tammy16_c03b2498:

    # tm "Ready to work out?"
    tm "Pronta para treinar?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:35
translate portuguese tammy16_81e72625:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do it!"
    pc "Sim, vamos a isso!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:46
translate portuguese tammy16b_d3127e62:

    # "Tonight is Tammy's fight. I better head over to the gym to support her."
    "Esta noite é a luta da Tammy. É melhor ir para o ginásio para a apoiar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:50
translate portuguese tammy16b_fc7a2349:

    # "The place is packed tonight. Even more people than the first fight. I guess everybody wants to see the rematch."
    "O lugar está lotado esta noite. Ainda mais gente do que na primeira luta. Acho que toda a gente quer ver a revanche."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:51
translate portuguese tammy16b_c1a9fded:

    # "I spot Tammy and Suzy hanging out near the ring and walk over to them."
    "Vejo a Tammy e a Suzy por perto do ringue e dirijo-me até elas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:54
translate portuguese tammy16b_ef965655:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. You in my corner again?"
    tm "Olá, [pcname]. Estás no meu canto outra vez?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:55
translate portuguese tammy16b_351f8f78:

    # pc "I'm always in your corner, girl."
    pc "Estou sempre no teu canto, miúda."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:58
translate portuguese tammy16b_7de5fb0a:

    # tm "I know you are. Love you!"
    tm "Eu sei que estás. Adoro-te!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:59
translate portuguese tammy16b_ce2ae2bf:

    # pc "Love you too."
    pc "Também te adoro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:60
translate portuguese tammy16b_fbdb8489:

    # "Chuck, the gym owner and referee, steps onto the stage and speaks into a microphone."
    "O Chuck, o dono do ginásio e árbitro, sobe ao palco e fala ao microfone."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:61
translate portuguese tammy16b_03a792fe:

    # "Chuck" "All right, everybody. Fighters to the ring."
    "Chuck" "Muito bem, pessoal. Lutadoras para o ringue."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:64
translate portuguese tammy16b_bc20373a:

    # tm "Guess I gotta go. Wish me luck."
    tm "Acho que tenho de ir. Desejem-me sorte."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:65
translate portuguese tammy16b_70969e05:

    # ss "You don't need it. You're going to wipe the mat with her."
    ss "Não precisas. Vais dar-lhe uma coça."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:66
translate portuguese tammy16b_8407fcdb:

    # pc "You trained so hard. You're a beast."
    pc "Treinaste tanto. És uma fera."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:67
translate portuguese tammy16b_0fc82d62:

    # tm "Thanks, guys."
    tm "Obrigada, pessoal."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:70
translate portuguese tammy16b_4d3281d1:

    # ss "You better get up there in her corner. She needs you."
    ss "É melhor subires para o canto dela. Ela precisa de ti."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:71
translate portuguese tammy16b_2cda7690:

    # pc "You don't want to?"
    pc "Não queres ir?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:72
translate portuguese tammy16b_2475c65e:

    # ss "No, I'm going to go cheer from the back. I don't like to see her get hit."
    ss "Não, vou torcer lá atrás. Não gosto de a ver a levar porrada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:73
translate portuguese tammy16b_7ebf9a37:

    # ss "But you'll hear me, I'm sure."
    ss "Mas vais ouvir-me, tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:76
translate portuguese tammy16b_8ba7b5ed:

    # "I climb up into Tammy's corner as Chuck introduces the fighters."
    "Subo para o canto da Tammy enquanto o Chuck apresenta as lutadoras."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:77
translate portuguese tammy16b_263516ea:

    # "Sara Death looks somehow even bigger and more jacked than she did last time they fought."
    "A Sara Death parece, de alguma forma, ainda maior e mais musculosa do que da última vez que lutaram."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:78
translate portuguese tammy16b_dd7b01f4:

    # "Tammy is so much smaller it's sometimes hard to believe that she can take an opponent like that down."
    "A Tammy é tão mais pequena que às vezes é difícil acreditar que consiga derrubar uma adversária assim."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:79
translate portuguese tammy16b_edae56fc:

    # "Chuck" "... Our return opponent in this rematch, Sara Death!"
    "Chuck" "... A nossa adversária nesta revanche, a Sara Death!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:83
translate portuguese tammy16b_a31e4957:

    # "Chuck" "And in this corner, undefeated so far in her amateur fighting career and hoping to continue that streak tonight..."
    "Chuck" "E neste canto, até agora invicta na sua carreira de lutadora amadora e na esperança de continuar essa série esta noite..."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:85
translate portuguese tammy16b_83b35d9b:

    # "Chuck" "And in this corner, looking to get revenge on the beating she took last fight..."
    "Chuck" "E neste canto, à procura de vingança pela derrota que sofreu no último combate..."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:86
translate portuguese tammy16b_96ba703d:

    # "Chuck" "... standing five-foot-six-inches tall and weighing in at 130 pounds..."
    "Chuck" "... com 1,68 m de altura e pesando 59 kg..."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:87
translate portuguese tammy16b_ec4b18ff:

    # "Chuck" "Tammy \"Wham! Bam!\" Zamora!"
    "Chuck" "Tammy «Wham! Bam!» Zamora!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:90
translate portuguese tammy16b_6f4f75f7:

    # "Chuck takes them to the middle of the ring and goes over the rules with them."
    "Chuck leva-as para o centro do ringue e repassa as regras com elas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:91
translate portuguese tammy16b_0b6f40cb:

    # "Sara smiles the whole time. I can see Sara and Tammy muttering something to each other and laughing."
    "A Sara sorri o tempo todo. Vejo a Sara e a Tammy a murmurarem algo uma para a outra e a rirem-se."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:92
translate portuguese tammy16b_24d8b054:

    # "Even though they're about to beat the crap out of each other, it seems like they're having a good time."
    "Apesar de estarem prestes a dar-se porrada uma à outra, parece que se estão a divertir."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:93
translate portuguese tammy16b_1b6ae11e:

    # "When they're done, they touch gloves and return to their corners."
    "Quando terminam, tocam as luvas e regressam aos seus cantos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:96
translate portuguese tammy16b_fcfdafdf:

    # pc "You got this."
    pc "Tu consegues."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:97
translate portuguese tammy16b_3caaf546:

    # tm "You're goddamn right."
    tm "Podes ter a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:98
translate portuguese tammy16b_0929120c:

    # "Chuck" "Three... Two... One... FIGHT!"
    "Chuck" "Três... Dois... Um... LUTA!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:101
translate portuguese tammy16b_ec9b5571:

    # "They both rush to the middle of the ring and the crowd goes wild."
    "Ambas correm para o centro do ringue e a multidão enlouquece."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:104
translate portuguese tammy16b_679f2669:

    # "Even over the yells of all of those around me, I can hear Suzy in the back, cheering loudly for our girlfriend."
    "Mesmo por cima dos gritos de todos à minha volta, consigo ouvir a Suzy lá atrás, a torcer em voz alta pela nossa namorada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:107
translate portuguese tammy16b_647f4a54:

    # "They circle around each other a bit, testing out their range, looking for openings."
    "Elas dão algumas voltas uma à volta da outra, a testar o alcance, à procura de aberturas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:110
translate portuguese tammy16b_5d7efc88:

    # "Tammy is trying to stay loose, moving in and out quickly to land leg kicks."
    "A Tammy tenta manter-se solta, avançando e recuando rapidamente para acertar pontapés nas pernas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:111
translate portuguese tammy16b_e3d4107b:

    # "She knows that getting too close would mean that she could be taken down to the ground."
    "Ela sabe que aproximar-se demasiado significaria que poderia ser derrubada para o chão."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:112
translate portuguese tammy16b_a88a4b4f:

    # "Having the much larger Sara on top of her could easily lead to her getting overwhelmed."
    "Ter a Sara, muito maior do que ela, em cima dela poderia facilmente levá-la a ser dominada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:115
translate portuguese tammy16b_a3883dc3:

    # "Of course, taking one of those big fists on her chin could knock her down as well."
    "Claro que levar um daqueles punhos enormes no queixo também poderia derrubá-la."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:116
translate portuguese tammy16b_b3da4826:

    # "Every second she's in this fight, there's more of a chance of her getting hit and knocked out."
    "A cada segundo que ela está nesta luta, há mais hipóteses de ser atingida e nocauteada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:119
translate portuguese tammy16b_cdd3604c:

    # "Tammy is able to land a few good hits, but Sara just takes them and keeps coming."
    "A Tammy consegue acertar alguns bons golpes, mas a Sara simplesmente aguenta-os e continua a avançar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:122
translate portuguese tammy16b_248b11e5:

    # "Then the referee calls the end of the round and steps in to separate them back to their corners."
    "Então, o árbitro anuncia o fim do assalto e intervém para as separar e mandá-las de volta aos seus cantos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:125
translate portuguese tammy16b_5dca43c0:

    # tm "How am I looking out there?"
    tm "Como estou a parecer aí?"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:126
translate portuguese tammy16b_40609e22:

    # pc "You look great. Really fucking sexy."
    pc "Estás ótima. Realmente muito sexy."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:127
translate portuguese tammy16b_4586870d:

    # tm "Haha, I need a real coach."
    tm "Haha, preciso de um treinador a sério."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:128
translate portuguese tammy16b_4e5ec89e:

    # pc "Seriously, you're looking good. Moving fast. Staying on your toes."
    pc "A sério, estás a ir bem. A mover-te rapidamente. A manter-te alerta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:129
translate portuguese tammy16b_eafbc9cd:

    # pc "I liked those leg kicks. They seemed to slow her down a bit. Her being slow is good. You can take advantage of that."
    pc "Gostei daqueles pontapés nas pernas. Pareceram abrandá-la um pouco. O facto de ela ser lenta é bom. Podes tirar partido disso."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:130
translate portuguese tammy16b_2d3b068d:

    # pc "Just be careful about her taking you down."
    pc "Tem apenas cuidado para que ela não te derrube."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:131
translate portuguese tammy16b_ec4282cb:

    # tm "Yeah, that's what I'm scared of. I've never been on the ground with her before."
    tm "Sim, é disso que tenho medo. Nunca estive no chão com ela antes."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:132
translate portuguese tammy16b_6ef7cd76:

    # pc "You got this. I'm pretty sure you won that first round. Just keep moving and stay hard to hit."
    pc "Tu consegues. Tenho quase a certeza de que ganhaste aquele primeiro assalto. Continua a mexer-te e mantém-te difícil de acertar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:133
translate portuguese tammy16b_850254f5:

    # tm "You got it. Thanks, coach."
    tm "Entendi. Obrigada, treinador."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:136
translate portuguese tammy16b_2221ccc4:

    # "When the bell rings, they're right back in the middle of the ring again, trading punches."
    "Quando o gongo soa, elas estão de volta ao meio do ringue, trocando socos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:137
translate portuguese tammy16b_c6a976b0:

    # "Tammy is able to block most of Sara's punches and sneak in a few of her own."
    "A Tammy consegue bloquear a maioria dos socos da Sara e dar alguns dela."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:140
translate portuguese tammy16b_9dbf1b1c:

    # "Then Tammy hops back and gets another hard kick to Sara's leg, the slap of shin on thigh echoing through the gym."
    "Depois, a Tammy salta para trás e dá outro pontapé forte na perna da Sara, o barulho da canela a bater na coxa ecoando pelo ginásio."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:141
translate portuguese tammy16b_4c60ba4c:

    # "Sara winces. That one hurt."
    "Sara estremece. Aquele doeu."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:144
translate portuguese tammy16b_e41ad8f5:

    # "The pain and the frustration gets to Sara then and she growls in anger as she charges forward."
    "A dor e a frustração tomam conta de Sara e ela rosna de raiva enquanto avança."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:145
translate portuguese tammy16b_03576045:

    # "She's throwing haymakers now, backing Tammy up towards the ropes."
    "Agora está a dar socos violentos, empurrando Tammy para as cordas."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:146
translate portuguese tammy16b_028976a4:

    # "Sara has lost all defense in this moment. If Tammy could take advantage of it, she might be able to end the fight."
    "Sara perdeu toda a defesa neste momento. Se Tammy conseguisse tirar partido disso, talvez conseguisse acabar com a luta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:149
translate portuguese tammy16b_5dc11d33:

    # "But then one of the punches connects, cracking against Tammy's jaw and rolling her eyes back."
    "Mas então um dos socos acerta, batendo com força na mandíbula de Tammy e fazendo-a revirar os olhos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:150
translate portuguese tammy16b_ade70eed:

    # "I hear Suzy in the back cry out in shock as Tammy falls to the mat."
    "Ouço a Suzy lá atrás gritar de choque quando a Tammy cai no tapete."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:153
translate portuguese tammy16b_76769a9d:

    # "At first, I think that's it, that Tammy is knocked out, but she quickly shakes her head and starts fighting back."
    "A princípio, penso que acabou, que a Tammy está nocauteada, mas ela rapidamente abana a cabeça e começa a ripostar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:154
translate portuguese tammy16b_8cf6bab3:

    # "But now Sara is on top of her, raining punches down onto her."
    "Mas agora a Sara está em cima dela, a fazer chover socos sobre ela."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:155
translate portuguese tammy16b_f5522b72:

    # "Chuck is close and I can tell he's about to stop the fight."
    "O Chuck está perto e percebo que está prestes a parar a luta."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:158
translate portuguese tammy16b_12ebb29b:

    # "What happens next is so fast that I can barely follow it."
    "O que acontece a seguir é tão rápido que mal consigo acompanhar."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:159
translate portuguese tammy16b_a46fd698:

    # "Tammy grabs Sara's wrist and bucks her hips, moving her legs up towards Sara's head."
    "A Tammy agarra o pulso da Sara e empurra com as ancas, levantando as pernas em direção à cabeça da Sara."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:162
translate portuguese tammy16b_14e97ff6:

    # "Then Tammy rotates and has Sara's arm fully stretched out."
    "Depois, a Tammy gira e estica completamente o braço da Sara."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:163
translate portuguese tammy16b_ca12b0e7:

    # "Sara cries out in pain. If she doesn't tap soon, Tammy could easily break her arm."
    "A Sara grita de dor. Se ela não desistir em breve, a Tammy pode facilmente partir-lhe o braço."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:166
translate portuguese tammy16b_f3df8ee4:

    # "She reluctantly taps and the crowd goes insane."
    "Ela desiste relutantemente e a multidão enlouquece."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:169
translate portuguese tammy16b_2d3791c3:

    # "I can't hear anything, the room is so loud and suddenly Suzy is right there, jumping up onto my shoulder."
    "Não consigo ouvir nada, a sala está tão barulhenta e, de repente, a Suzy está mesmo ali, a saltar para o meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:170
translate portuguese tammy16b_be32fa84:

    # "I hold her high while she cheers."
    "Seguro-a no ar enquanto ela aplaude."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:173
translate portuguese tammy16b_411f816b:

    # "Chuck announces the winner, but it's impossible to hear him over the roaring crowd."
    "O Chuck anuncia a vencedora, mas é impossível ouvi-lo por cima do rugido da multidão."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:174
translate portuguese tammy16b_67d97e00:

    # "Tammy and Sara are both crying in the ring. Suzy's crying on my shoulder. Hell, I'm crying a little bit too."
    "A Tammy e a Sara estão ambas a chorar no ringue. A Suzy está a chorar no meu ombro. Raios, eu também estou a chorar um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:177
translate portuguese tammy16b_09e2a5ca:

    # "Then Tammy runs over and kisses Suzy."
    "Depois, a Tammy corre e beija a Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:178
translate portuguese tammy16b_5354153a:

    # ss "You're a fucking queen! I love you!"
    ss "És uma raia de rainha! Adoro-te!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:179
translate portuguese tammy16b_4039bf0e:

    # tm "I love both of you so fucking much!"
    tm "Adoro-vos às duas tanto!"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:182
translate portuguese tammy16b_c191fa62:

    # "The next half hour passes by in a blur as everybody congratulates Tammy and wants to talk to her and Sara."
    "A meia hora seguinte passa num borrão, enquanto toda a gente felicita a Tammy e quer falar com ela e com a Sara."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:183
translate portuguese tammy16b_693b77ad:

    # "I hear them already planning another fight. Maybe in Whiterock next time."
    "Ouço-as já a planear outro combate. Talvez em Whiterock da próxima vez."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:187
translate portuguese tammy16b_3c502a36:

    # "Eventually the gym clears out. Tammy and Sara head back to the showers together, while Suzy and I wait up front for her."
    "Por fim, o ginásio esvazia-se. A Tammy e a Sara dirigem-se juntas para os chuveiros, enquanto a Suzy e eu esperamos por ela à entrada."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:188
translate portuguese tammy16b_559ff5f9:

    # ss "Tonight was crazy."
    ss "Esta noite foi de loucos."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:189
translate portuguese tammy16b_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Pois."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:190
translate portuguese tammy16b_90a33a46:

    # ss "I've never seen her take a punch that hard. That was scary."
    ss "Nunca a vi levar um soco tão forte. Foi assustador."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:191
translate portuguese tammy16b_a0a77eb7:

    # ss "She's going to be really sore later. We might have to make her feel good back at home."
    ss "Ela vai ficar com muitas dores mais tarde. Talvez tenhamos de a fazer sentir-se bem quando chegarmos a casa."

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy16.rpy:192
